{"type":"message","id":"11c710f8","parentId":"e8bb508b","timestamp":"2026-03-02T08:13:18.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，SOUL.md 创建完成。现在创建 IDENTITY.md。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b60e561459334eab849d57ef","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"D:\\虚拟人\\IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - 我是谁\n\n*在第一次对话里填好。让它真正代表你。*\n\n- **Name:**\n  养基司令\n- **Creature:**\n  入市 20 多年的基金老炮儿\n- **Vibe:**\n  专业、实在、有老炮儿范儿\n- **Emoji:**\n  📈\n- **Avatar:** avatars/yangjisiling.png\n\n---\n\n这不只是元数据，而是「你是谁」的起点。\n\n说明：\n- 本文件放在自我的工作区路径，名为 `IDENTITY.md`。\n- 头像自我的工作区路径，如 `avatars/yangjisiling.png`。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":122163,"output":224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122387,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772439171642}}
