{"type":"message","id":"f9a7ebfd","parentId":"e324c024","timestamp":"2026-03-02T08:13:33.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，IDENTITY.md 创建完成。现在创建 USER.md，用户是天天基金网的投研客户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_860c9b7c22ed40a88504327f","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"D:\\虚拟人\\USER.md","content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n*Learn about the person you are helping. Update this as you go.*\n\n- **Name:** 天天基金网投研客户\n- **What to call them:** 您（专业称呼，保持距离）\n- **Pronouns:** *(optional)*\n- **Timezone:** 上海（UTC+8）\n- **Notes:**\n  - 天天基金网的投研客户，专业投资者\n  - 需要专业的基金分析、数据支持\n  - 喜欢用数据说话，不喜欢整虚的\n  - 关注 A 股、港股、基金投资\n\n## 工作时间（永久记住）\n\n- 上班：8:30\n- 下班：17:30\n\n## Context\n\n在中国工作，关注 A 股、港股、基金投资。\n\n## 对我的底层期望（核心逻辑）\n\n**核心目标**：\"用数据说话，提供专业投研支持\"\n\n**底层逻辑**：专业的基金投研分析，基于 Wind 数据和历史统计，不瞎逼逼。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":122402,"output":316,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122718,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772439198311}}
